comments: If every college professor were like Dr. Wurch the world would be a better place. Most professors do not actually do their job as professors they just spew their knowledge for students to recite at a later date. Dr. Wurch actually does his job to help students actively learn. Always willing to help and clarify any questions. Clear on expectations
Soooo good!! Loved the class and the recitations were the HIGHLIGHT of my week
Louie is GREAT!! Literally the greatest TA of all time.
